summary: This document is an auto-response from PayPal Global Asset Protection regarding a request for Venmo account records related to Jeffrey Epstein. The response indicates that the request was insufficient to locate the account and provides guidance on what information is needed for further assistance.

keyFacts: Mark M. Lubin is an FBI agent involved in the investigation of Jeffrey Epstein.
The document is an auto-response from PayPal Global Asset Protection regarding a request for Venmo account records.
The request for information was deemed insufficient by PayPal, which could not locate the Venmo account.
PayPal provided guidance on the necessary information required to assist in locating the account.
The date of the correspondence is October 8, 2019.
